subsection.p:
When s=0,

  \boxed{
  \frac{\partial}{\partial t}
  \bigl(\rho\,dx\wedge dy\wedge dz\bigr)
  +
  d\Phi_{\mathbf J}
  =
  0.
  }

This is the same conservation sentence again:

  \boxed{
  \text{time-change of stored amount}
  +
  \text{spatial derivative of flux}
  =
  \text{source}.
  }
